  Project 3 – Implementation for REST API Endpoints using AWS Lambda

Region : Europe (Paris) - eu-west-3

API EndPoints :


• getAllCategory – fetch all the categories from the database.

https://ilrxkdww6e.execute-api.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com/P3_HARITHA_API_DEPLOYMENT/api/getAllCategory


• getCategoryName - given the category id fetch the name of the category


https://ilrxkdww6e.execute-api.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com/P3_HARITHA_API_DEPLOYMENT/api/getCategoryName?categoryId=1001


• getCategoryId - fetch the ID of the category with the given category name


https://ilrxkdww6e.execute-api.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com/P3_HARITHA_API_DEPLOYMENT/api/getCategoryId?categoryName=Classics


• addCategory - add the given category, with category Id and category name, in the database.


https://ilrxkdww6e.execute-api.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com/P3_HARITHA_API_DEPLOYMENT/api/addCategory


• getAllBook - fetch all the books from the database

https://ilrxkdww6e.execute-api.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com/P3_HARITHA_API_DEPLOYMENT/api/getAllBook


• getBookById – fetch the book given the book id.

https://ilrxkdww6e.execute-api.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com/P3_HARITHA_API_DEPLOYMENT/api/getBookById?bookId=1001


• getBookByCategoryId - fetch all books of the given category id


https://ilrxkdww6e.execute-api.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com/P3_HARITHA_API_DEPLOYMENT/api/getBookByCategoryId?categoryId=1001


• getBookByCategoryName - fetch all books of the given category name

https://ilrxkdww6e.execute-api.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com/P3_HARITHA_API_DEPLOYMENT/api/getBookByCategoryName?categoryName=Classics



• getRandomBook - fetch 5 random books from the database

https://ilrxkdww6e.execute-api.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com/P3_HARITHA_API_DEPLOYMENT/api/getRandomBook


• addBook – add the book in the database given the book information

https://ilrxkdww6e.execute-api.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com/P3_HARITHA_API_DEPLOYMENT/api/addBook

